headline: Unlocking Q2 Potential of Conagra Brands (CAG): Exploring Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Conagra Brands (CAG), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended November 2024.

headline: Conagra Brands adds ‘GLP-1 friendly’ label to some Healthy Choice meals
summary: The marketing initiative touts the protein and fiber content of the offerings, which appeals to consumers taking weight-loss medications such as Ozempic and Wegovy.
